last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 10
last_episode_to_air.overview: It's back to fighting form for the grand finale dinner; Kyla wants an apology; Janet's not even sure she'll show up; Kyla invites drag artist Paris, but which queen will reign supreme?

name: The Real Housewives of Melbourne
overview: Follow the busy, aspirational lifestyles of a group of driven and ambitious women who enjoy the lavish, pampered and cultured lifestyle of Melbourne. Between them, they own private jets, amazing homes and are married to high profile businessmen, including one to a rock star and another to a plastic surgeon.

seasons.name: Season 4
seasons.overview: The Real Housewives of Melbourne follows the busy, aspirational lifestyles of a group of driven and ambitious women who enjoy the lavish, pampered and cultured lifestyle of Melbourne. Between them, they own private jets, amazing homes and are married to high profile businessmen, including one to a rock star and another to a plastic surgeon.

seasons.name: Season 5
seasons.overview:
Fans of The Real Housewives of Melbourne cracked open the champagne early last year when it was announced the series would start filming a fifth season of the hit reality series, with three new faces stepping up to join the mayhem!

However, with the outbreak of COVID-19, filming unfortunately came to a halt faster than it takes to clutch your pearls during a RHOM dinner party, and we all had to put that celebratory sparkling wine back in the fridge. Until now!

So bring out the canapes, as it’s been announced today that cameras are rolling again – with a couple of surprises when it comes to the cast!

episodes.name: First Impressions
episodes.overview: A new glamorous group of Real Housewives is set to take Australia by storm! The Real Housewives of Melbourne follow six sophisticated ladies who enjoy the lavish pampered and cultured lifestyle of Melbourne.

episodes.name: Pick a Side
episodes.overview: After Jackie's psychic reading Gina heads to the States to see her partner. Chyka invites the wives to a food tasting at historic Mural Hall.

episodes.name: New Kids on the Block
episodes.overview: Janet visits Dr Chris Moss for some 'freshening' and asks her new bestie Jackie along for support. Jackie and Ben host an extravagant housewarming party but when Ben confronts Gina about her issues with his wife, things go south.

episodes.name: Ice Queens
episodes.overview: Lydia invites Jackie and Andrea away for skiing in Thredbo, they bond on and off the slopes. Back in Melbourne, Chyka and Gina help Janet chose outfits for her date that night with a younger man. Could this be a new love?

episodes.name: Birthday Girl
episodes.overview: Bruce manages to steal Chyka away for a romantic date night. Janet celebrates her birthday by picking up her sparkling three carat diamond ring. Later that day, another Housewife threatens to take the shine off her party.

episodes.name: Anyone For Tennis?
episodes.overview: The new Liberty Belle Skin Centre building is slow as Andrea anxiously plans a launch party. Andrea hosts a tennis day at her beach house on the Mornington Peninsula. It starts off well but its game on when one of the girls arrives late.

episodes.name: Travelling North
episodes.overview: In the hope of repairing some burnt bridges between the girls, Chyka invites everyone to the stunning Elandra resort at Mission Beach, Qld, where they'll have the entire place to themselves. The breathtaking helicopter ride there provides a welcome distraction from the growing tension that's bound to boil over sooner or later. The backdrop may be glamorous but look out Gina, these women mean business.

episodes.name: No Show or Go Show?
episodes.overview: The ladies return from Mission Beach with more baggage than they started out with and all somewhat stunned at the turn of events. Can Chyka's fancy soiree at Luminare iron things out and will Gina even show up?

episodes.name: Pooch Party
episodes.overview: Chyka hosts an elaborate pooch party for the girls and their fur-children. At a party Lydia questions Janet about something Gina divulged. Keen to get to the bottom of it, Janet meets Gina for a drink and things quickly turn sour.

episodes.name: Here's to Happy Endings
episodes.overview: Jackie and Ben audition dancers for the launch. Andrea shoots the cover of her upcoming book. Chyka encourages Gina and Andrea to meet and discuss their differences but are they ready to be civil before the big La Mascara launch party?

episodes.name: Reunion - Part 1
episodes.overview: Alex Perry hosts this drama filled reunion, as the housewives come together to discuss the series, their relationships and also the contents of that frequently talked about email!

episodes.name: Reunion - Part 2
episodes.overview: The housewives continue to discuss the highs and lows of the series, the accusations, the Chinese whispers and everyone's favourite pampered pooch - Figaro.

episodes.name: Fresh Start, New Faces
episodes.overview: Jackie, Lydia and Chyka meet up for lunch while Janet organizes her birthday party. The housewives attend Janets birthday party and we are introduced to two new housewives, Gamble Breaux and Pettifluer Berenger.

episodes.name: Murder Mystery Party
episodes.overview: Pettifluer wants to buy a Bentley. Gamble trains her dog cash. Gamble is hosting a murder mystery party and has invited all the housewives. Jackie, Janet and Pettifluer try on costumes for the party and Pettifluer is being rude to the shop assistant. Gamble and Rick get engaged and announce it at her Murder Mystery Party. Janet, Chyka and Gamble meet up for lunch and Chyka brings up a conversation about rumors and Janet says that Gamble was a stripper and a call girl.

episodes.name: Fashion Flare Up
episodes.overview: Jackie promotes her cocktail brand, LaMascara. Jackie, Janet, Gina and Gamble attend the Chadstone fashion show. Gamble confronts Janet. Lydia learns to play poker with Shane Warne for a charity.

episodes.name: Anyone for Golf?
episodes.overview: Gina and Janet catch up for coffee. Gina brings up the rumors and Janet walks out. Janet invites Gamble, Jackie, Gamble and Gina for golf. Jackie and Janet go look for outfits for golf and Janet brings up the lunch with Gina. The girls go to the mornington peninsula to play golf. Jackie says that Gina will loose her golf stick, and Gina does loose her stick. Gamble and Janet call a truce.

episodes.name: Chef's Dinner
episodes.overview: Chyka, Jackie and Pettifluer go for lunch and Pettifluer calls Gamble stupid. Chyka invites everyone for a dinner. Lydia comes back from Italy, where her son gets married. While Lydia tells a heart-breaking story, Gamble starts laughing. Gamble confronts Pettifluer about calling her stupid. Gamble and Janet start arguing about the rumors.

episodes.name: Look Out Sydney
episodes.overview: Everyone attends the AFL Grand Final, except Gina and Jackie. Gamble invites Gina, Janet and Pettifleur to Sydney. Lydia confronts Gamble about when she laughed at the dinner. The ladies go to Sydney and attend the Billich Art Gallery. Gambles sister, Tempest confronts Janet about the rumors. Janet walks out of the Art Gallery and Gina and Gamble try to get her back in. Everyone goes for dinner and makes a pack that they don't bring up the rumors again. Gina has a few digs against Pettifluer.

episodes.name: Manila Bound
episodes.overview: Chyka and Jackie look for a venue for Gambles hens party. Janet invites everyone to Manila. The ladies arrive at Manila. Chyka, Gamble and Gina go for lunch and talk about Pettifluer controversial book, Switch the Bitch. The housewives go for dinner and Gina and Pettifluer come to blows when Pettifluers book comes up.

episodes.name: Philippines Part 2
episodes.overview: Gamble and Pettifluer has an argument when Pettifluer says that Gina is racist. Jackie and Gamble have an argument when Jackie says that Gina knew about the rumors and she said that she was going to throw the newbies under the bus. Jackie and Gina have an argument and the argument escalates and get into a screaming match. The housewives go for drinks at the hotel bar and Gamble and Petttifluer have an disagreement.

episodes.name: Gina's New Shoes
episodes.overview: Janet launches her tea range. Gamble and Janets friend Carlos get into an argument about the rumors. Gina launches her new shoes. Janet and Pettifluer are upset that she named a shoe about them. Jackie has a party launching her LaMascara High-Tea.

episodes.name: A Day at the Races
episodes.overview: Gamble and Rick buys a engagement ring. The housewives attend the Spring Racing Carnival. Pettifluer launches her book. Gamble and Gina confront Pettifluer about the book again. Jackie disagrees with Gamble and Gina. Gamble has her hens night. Jackie and Chyka organized strippers. Gina said to Gamble that Gambles make-up artist started about rumors. Janet and Gamble get into another argument about the rumors.

episodes.name: Wonderland
episodes.overview: Pettifluer and Chyka organized Pettifluers 50th birthday. Manuela, Janet and Gamble get into an argument about the rumors. Gina and Jackie gets into an argument and Jackie pushes the door and gets into a screaming match on the balcony with Gina.

episodes.name: Reunion - Part 1
episodes.overview: The housewives reunite to talk about the second season.

episodes.name: Reunion - Part 2
episodes.overview: The housewives reunite to talk about the second season.

episodes.name: Join The Club
episodes.overview: It's great to see all the women are back but the new girl Susie must be wondering what planet she's landed on after inviting them over for a baking day and a full on brawl ensues.

episodes.name: Old Sparks, New Starts
episodes.overview: Janet has dinner with her ex husband Brian, Gamble promotes her dress designer to wedding planner and Lydia's the hot topic of conversation when the women go horse riding.

episodes.name: By Invitation Only
episodes.overview: Gamble hosts a cocktail party where she plans to issue the wedding invitations. It's not exactly a sedate gathering as simmering tensions surface before all hell breaks loose.

episodes.name: Here Come the Brides
episodes.overview: Chyka throws Gamble a bridal shower with a twist thanks to the strict dress code: "wedding dresses only". Turn's out wearing your old frock can be an emotional trigger!

episodes.name: Gamble's Big Day
episodes.overview: The ladies head to Byron for Gamble's wedding. But with wild weather threatening the beach ceremony and everyone at logger heads, it's not exactly the smoothest of wedding days.

episodes.name: Bye Bye Byron
episodes.overview: Gina's early departure the night before the wedding turns the wives into reception detectives. Once back in Melbourne family's the focus with bitter sweet life lessons to confront.

episodes.name: Portrait Of Figaro
episodes.overview: Chyka hosts a glamourous middle eastern dinner to extend an exciting invitation to the ladies but the thrill is somewhat dampened when Pettifleur and Jackie start sparring.

episodes.name: Do Buy
episodes.overview: The housewives arrive in lavish, resplendent Dubai. But not even the world's largest shopping mall can curtail their bickering which is fuelled to boiling point by scorching desert temps.

episodes.name: Desert Storm
episodes.overview: After an impassioned dinner in the Dubai desert that frightens the camels, the wives recover over retail therapy in the souks before heading off to another explosive group dinner.

episodes.name: Gossip Girl
episodes.overview: As Dubai recovers from the high drama that accompanied the housewives on their trip, the women return to normality back home with family. But it's a normal only they understand.

episodes.name: Waterfront
episodes.overview: Lydia's mum celebrates her 69th birthday, Gina launches her perfume line and the ladies all get together for a final dramatic dinner come showdown at the Waterfront Restaurant.

episodes.name: Reunion
episodes.overview: After the most explosive series ever, temperatures soar as the ladies reunite for a fiery reunion that is sure to set tongues wagging. The Housewives air their grievances with tears, tantrums and allegations.

episodes.name: Venus Rising
episodes.overview: Gina and Lydia are closer than ever. The same can't be said for Gamble who finds herself increasingly on the outs. Jackie questions if Gina has replaced Gamble with new girl Venus?

episodes.name: House of Lords
episodes.overview: Gable vents to Janet and Jackie about her frustrations with Gina. The ladies also debrief on new girl Venus. Later, Janet meets with hotelier and Melbourne socialite Sally Bloomfield who is interested in stocking Janet's tea in her boutique hotel and wellness centre in Bali. The two hit it off and Janet invites her to meet the rest of the ladies and her cocktail party. Gamble causes a stir at Janet's party with her carefully planned gift, which manages to offend Venus and her husband James.

episodes.name: Midsummer Madness
episodes.overview: Janet, Jackie and Sally visit Chyka's new country estate and fill her in on all the goss. At Luke's Midsummer Night's Dream 21st party, Janet hears a disturbing rumour about Venus.

episodes.name: Dishing The Dirt
episodes.overview: On a day of truffle hunting in the country, Sally confronts Venus about the photos. Meanwhile Janet, Jackie and Gamble are determined to get to the bottom of the mystery surrounding Venus.

episodes.name: Sally Can't Wait
episodes.overview: Sally invites the girls to celebrate the launch of her accessories line, but things go a little pear shaped when Gamble and Venus lock horns and Lydia stirs things up with Jackie and Janet.

episodes.name: It's My Party I'll Invite Who I Want To
episodes.overview: The girls celebrate Jackie's 37th birthday in style, with the notable exception of Lydia. Jackie invites them on an overseas trip, motivating Venus to patch things up with Gamble.

episodes.name: Tequila Sunrise
episodes.overview: The Housewives arrive in beautiful Cabo San Lucas, Mexico, ready to kick up their heels and have some fun, but while 6 of them are sipping cocktails, Venus is back in Melbourne searching for her passport.

episodes.name: Tequila Sunset
episodes.overview: The housewives set sail for some fun in the sun on a catamaran off Cabo’s coast but, beneath the calm waters, a storm is brewing between Gina and Sally. At dinner that night, the girls put their differences aside and open up about past relationships, sharing the lessons they’ve learnt through heartache. But the love swiftly evaporates when Gina and Sally go head-to-head.

episodes.name: Getting Into The Spirit
episodes.overview: Jackie takes to the stage for her debut Shine It Up show in front of 300 eager fans. Venus holds a make-up masterclass showcasing her new contouring cosmetics, and reveals her true self. In an effort to bid farewell to the ghosts currently haunting her house, Gamble invites the girls to a seance.

episodes.name: Happy Birthday Baby
episodes.overview: Venus plans the ultimate fourth birthday party for her youngest daughter, Sophia. Jackie is the proud recipient of a great honour in her hometown of Newcastle. A nervous Gamble rehearses her surprise song for Rick, and Sally drops by for moral support. Sophia's party enchants even the most hardened housewives, but Gamble's attempt to compliment Venus backfires in her face.

episodes.name: The Great Divide
episodes.overview: Some forms of exercise are not for everyone and Sally vows never to return after she tries her first spin class with Jackie. Gamble finally reveals her anniversary surprise for Rick and her hard work pays off as it brings him to tears. The tears continue when Sally and her extended family scatter her husband Ian’s ashes. Lydia hosts a dinner for the girls and the night descends into chaos after Lydia attempts to say a few words about each of the girls.

episodes.name: Reunion
episodes.overview: The housewives come together with Alex Perry for the most explosive reunion yet. With bullying and body image on the agenda there are sure to be a few bombshells dropped.

4.name: Season 4
4.overview: The Real Housewives of Melbourne follows the busy, aspirational lifestyles of a group of driven and ambitious women who enjoy the lavish, pampered and cultured lifestyle of Melbourne. Between them, they own private jets, amazing homes and are married to high profile businessmen, including one to a rock star and another to a plastic surgeon.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: Excitement is at fever pitch as Jackie, Janet, and Gamble reunite in epic Housewives style. A somewhat hormonal Jackie is desperately trying to fall pregnant, and a tense exchange at a day spa gets heated.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Jackie confides in the ladies about her recent miscarriage and has a life-changing secret to share with husband Ben, before a drinking game turns sour at the Masterclass when Gamble accuses Anjali of peddling fake news.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: After a conflict-driven start, UN-level negotiations are under way to patch up the rifts in the group. Following an emotional scan of her twins, Jackie invites all on a luxurious and restorative 'babymoon'.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: The housewives are settling into a newly-pregnant Jackie's North Queensland 'babymoon' when Simone accuses Cherry of trying to steal her designer, and rumours abound Kyla's not being honest about her past.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: Jackie's wellbeing-inspired 'babymoon' has yet to bring calm. Simone and Cherry's squabble over a fashion designer continues, and back in Melbourne, the storm clouds part briefly before another conflict kicks off.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Gamble fulfils a lifelong ambition to celebrate her late father's art, but where is Anjali? Tempers flare when Gamble reveals the ex-CNN anchor's been accusing the ladies of fake news.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: A shocking rumour about Janet resurfaces, before Anjali makes a bombshell revelation of her own. Jackie's baby shower goes off with a bang as the gender of her twins is finally revealed by a double cannon fire.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Despite one glaring absence, the girls head out of town with high hopes for a tension-free weekend until a persistent rumour about Janet threatens the peace and one housewife makes another cataclysmic exit.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: The dust from Janet and Kyla's clash at Gamble's record launch has yet to settle, with Simone's alleged pot-stirring now in the spotlight too. Could another housewife soon be departing the group?

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: It's back to fighting form for the grand finale dinner; Kyla wants an apology; Janet's not even sure she'll show up; Kyla invites drag artist Paris, but which queen will reign supreme?

5.name: Season 5
5.overview:
Fans of The Real Housewives of Melbourne cracked open the champagne early last year when it was announced the series would start filming a fifth season of the hit reality series, with three new faces stepping up to join the mayhem!

However, with the outbreak of COVID-19, filming unfortunately came to a halt faster than it takes to clutch your pearls during a RHOM dinner party, and we all had to put that celebratory sparkling wine back in the fridge. Until now!

So bring out the canapes, as it’s been announced today that cameras are rolling again – with a couple of surprises when it comes to the cast!
